reviewText: Excellent movies! Great comedies, arrived right away, fantastic keep!
Role Models does not work at all. DVD player says "can't read". I would just return it, but for $7 it's hardly worth the time.
Product fit description and came fast
This pack has three of my favorite "newer" movies.  However, my package came with only 2 of the 3 movies despite the package being factory sealed.  I had to send it back.  Bummer.

The movies included are great, but this economy edition includes an incredibly annoying amount of outdated trailers loaded at the front of each disc. You cannot skip or fast-forward and they play every time. If you're the type who watches movies over and over, this gets old real fast. It was so bad we chucked this set in the trash, would actually rather replace each movie on Bluray for twice the cost each if it means no forced ads.
Looks like a cheap chinese bootleg, for the price I guess I can't complain too much. At least it played. Picture looks zoomed in, footage is blurry and grainy even for SD. DVD setup menu didn't work.
It was just as expected and played perfectly.
